comment: After the steal, Cousins (SAC) trips Noel (SAC) as he falls to the floor.
Casspi (SAC) makes contact with the arm of Grant (PHI) that affects his RSBQ.
Casspi (SAC) sets the screen on Smith (PHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Sampson (PHI) makes contact with Belinelli (SAC) that affects his RSBQ.
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Smith (PHI).
Noel (PHI) and Acy (SAC) briefly engage and separate on the missed free throw.
Grant (PHI) maintains legal guarding position as he jumps vertically to contest the shot attempt by Gay (SAC).
Collison (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Canaan's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Acy (SAC) and Noel (PHI) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Rondo (SAC) makes contact to the arm of Grant (PHI) that affects his RSBQ.
Casspi (SAC) commits the backcourt turnover when he throws the ball into the backcourt without it being deflected by a PHI player.
Casspi (SAC) commits a take foul on Covington (PHI).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was upheld.
